<p>Here is a definition similar to the one in <code>Data.List.All</code>:</p>  <pre><code>open import Data.Vec  data All {α π} {A : Set α} (P : A -&gt; Set π) : ∀ {n} -&gt; Vec A n -&gt; Set π where   []ₐ  : All P []   _∷ₐ_ : ∀ {n x} {xs : Vec A n} -&gt; P x -&gt; All P xs -&gt; All P (x ∷ xs) </code></pre>  <p>Why does <code>All</code> lie in <code>Set π</code>?</p>  <p>Agda version 2.4.3.</p>